:"2019-10-11T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"另外仲要美國線<br />\n<br />\n榮光盃 以波會友 撐morey<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646298</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStandWithMoreypeanut&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=e1704d83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/StandWithMoreypeanut</a>"},{"pid":"cfd73d4101619430f0bd0088e7ee810ca5b06e95","tid":1647120,"uid":169430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"手動推"},{"pid":"420db1a02cc757d9c7c8837fb664d9b4c9b44c31","tid":1647120,"uid":169430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bead2a9abad47db422f6a04f7b8cdcedc7ce4c0","tid":1647120,"uid":212037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:31:52.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe931cb958e7e171c6140814a6c9402f2fbb7a42","tid":1647120,"uid":169430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:49:11.000Z","msg":"【1012人鏈會議】<br />\n<br />\n一、討論細流<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; &mdash;<br />\n<br />\n公式時間（向傳媒公佈）1330-1500<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; &mdash;<br />\n<br />\n一點半集合&mdash;&mdash;兩點排人鏈&mdash;&mdash;默哀（學彤負責）&mdash;&mdash;唱歌&mdash;&mdash;叫口號&mdash;&mdash;至三點完結<br />\n<br />\n路線：由經貿辦到統一百貨方向圍圏<br />\n<br />\n邊青：咪、音箱<br />\n<br />\n東吳：負責單反相機、絲帶<br />\n<br />\n文大、政大：口罩<br />\n<br />\n東吳、文大：工作人員x4<br />\n<br />\n文大：注音歌詞x50<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二、公關討論<br />\n<br />\n刪除聯訪<br />\n<br />\n新聞稿更動（加上緊急法、1012活動目的）<br />\n<br />\n三、公關口調<br />\n<br />\n假如被無約訪記者採訪：可用東吳文宣做intenal use或用新聞稿作回應主軸<br />\n<br />\n四大重點：<br />\n1.回應活動是記念612的佔領運動<br />\n2.回應警方暴力行為、濫暴，以及政府的處理方法<br />\n3.提及緊急法<br />\n4.聲援香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四、宣傳共識<br />\n<br />\n邊青：文宣開po宣傳活動1830-2100由其他學校關注組轉載<br />\n<br />\n各學校關注組自行製造文宣、或可使用tg內的文宣<br />\n<br />\n做人鏈平面圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五、人鏈後合作討論<br />\n<br />\n派1-3個代表<br />\n<br />\n北科大（人多）或統一百貨food court（人少）討論後續"}]}